Package edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.application

Class Application

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.application.Application
public class Application extends Object
The Application class handles the Application object and holds Application (context), AppState (interface) and the 6 concrete state classes.
Author:
Anoushka Piduru
